{"tid":834373,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[爆卦] 【中國幼兒園又出大事了】","createTime":"2018-09-24T07:10:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-24T11:13:16.000Z","uid":25345,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"bd2e5fc64d49a11b01eeab236f2e23d538b895f6","tid":834373,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T07:10:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/Gossiping/M.1537761445.A.4F9.html\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ptt.cc%2Fbbs%2FGossiping%2FM.1537761445.A.4F9.html&h=fb27619a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n 腐爛雞腿/發霉大米/過期調味料，家長到醫院幫小孩身體檢查，多人罹患癌症。昨天家長 想上訪南京政府，全部被公安攔截，待遇跟之前老兵上訪一樣。唉.....可憐阿!<br />\n<br />\n 中國的小孩真可憐，出生先要擔心疫苗，幼兒園/小學要擔心食品安全，還有性侵問題。 高中大學還要擔心言論自由，一輩子都要活的小心翼翼。<br />\n<br />\n 昨天到現在，中國官媒都是瑞典辱支新聞，要求道歉。 國內出事，就用國家民族大義來掩蓋囉！"},{"pid":"49efad9632c28f8dd808f040d8537d4d1fd82101","tid":834373,"uid":25345,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T07:10:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/Gossiping/M.1537761445.A.4F9.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ptt.cc%2Fbbs%2FGossiping%2FM.1537761445.A.4F9.html&d=I351fSihAHQRxhP70sHOzLIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=c653699a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/Gossiping/M.1537761445.A.4F9.html</a>"},{"pid":"c19e529672652ac49ed7c4adee45ce7e1905b6aa","tid":834373,"uid":153811,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T07:15:03.000Z","msg":"唔出事就真係大事"},{"pid":"c0d3a80a84a37b67812e603d163af20fc8167d79","tid":834373,"uid":30377,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T07:16:42.000Z","msg":"冇新聞就真係新聞"},{"pid":"1468eeb73d6c1d7ca12fbc541ecdd430e3c201b0","tid":834373,"uid":63154,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T07:18:06.000Z","msg":"人類底線<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01241a6671b2ad8434285676b6f1690221699370","tid":834373,"uid":62532,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score